Simmons Airlines Inc said its board ofdirectors authorized a doubling in the company's stockrepurchase program to one mln shares from 500,000 shares.    The buyback would represent about 20 pct of its issuedshares, Simmons said.    The company said it bought 205,000 shares today, bringingits total repurchase since the program was authorized on July29 to 534,500 shares. It said Simmons now has 4,540,459 sharesoutstanding. Its stock closed at 5-5/8 bid and 5-3/4 offered.    Shares will be bought privately and in the open market, itsaid. Reuter&#3;